<p>The Navigation bar pattern displays a primary horizonal and optional secondary navigation.</p>

<h2>Usage</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Each menu should contains 5-8 links</li>
</ul>

<h2>Syntax</h2>

<div class="pattern-source">{{> navigation-bar navigation-bar-2}}</div>


<h2>Options</h2>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Secondary navigation</strong><br>
        Secondary navigation is achieved by using the same pattern for primary, but adding a <code>secondary</code> class to the main element.
    </li>
</ul>
